Class Project

java.lang.Object
main.model.project.Project
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Project extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a Build-To-Order (BTO) project in the BTO Management System. A project contains information such as its name, neighborhood, flat types, application period, assigned manager, officer slots, and related applications and enquiries.
Since:
2025-04-16
